Description_lang: As Phantasmal Bloodfangs die, an Essence of Night is created. This effect increases all damage and healing by $s1% as long as players are within the Illusionary Night. In addition, mana regeneration is increased by $s3%.This effect persists for 30 sec after exiting the illusion.
AuraDescription_lang: All damage and healing increased by $s1%.Mana regeneration increased by $s3%.
